Installing sqlgrey:
-------------------

No need to run initial 'make'. Just run:

make install

To install with init-script, prepend
your distro to 'install' like this:
-----------------------------------
make rh-install (redhat)
make gentoo-install  
make debian-install


With DBCluster support:
-----------------------
make use_dbcluster
make install

Revert back to DBI (from dbcluster):
------------------------------------
make use_dbi
make install



Now go read HOWTO..
